#* Right-click in the [[3D_View|3D View]] and select the {{MenuCommand|[[Image:Sketcher_ViewSketch.svg|16px]] View sketch}} option from the context menu.
#* Use the keyboard shortcut: {{KEY|Q}} then {{KEY|P}}.


